{"name": "indico-plugin-cloud-captchas", "metadata": {"name": "indico-plugin-cloud-captchas", "version": "3.3.1", "classifiers": ["Environment :: Plugins", "Environment :: Web Environment", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["indico"], "summary": "Google reCAPTCHA plugin for Indico", "upload_time": 1733157533}, "documentation": ["# Cloud CAPTCHAs Plugin\n\nThis plugin replaces the built-in CAPTCHA with Google's reCAPTCHA v2 or hCaptcha.\n\nThis plugin also serves as an example for developers who want to use a different\nCAPTCHA for their Indico instance.\n\n![screenshot](recaptcha.png)\n\n\n## Setup\n\nThe plugin requires you to set the site key and secret key on the plugin settings page.\n\nWhen using reCaptcha these keys can be created on the [reCAPTCHA admin dashboard][recaptcha-create].\nChoose **reCAPTCHA v2** and **\"I'm not a robot\" Checkbox**.\n\nWhen using hCaptcha the keys can be created on the [hCaptcha dashboard][hcaptcha-dashboard].\n\n## Changelog\n\n### 3.3.1\n\n- Update translations\n\n### 3.3\n\n- Support (and require) Python 3.12\n\n### 3.2.1\n\n- Support Python 3.11\n\n### 3.2\n\n- Initial release for Indico 3.2\n\n[recaptcha-create]: https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin/create\n[hcaptcha-dashboard]: https://dashboard.hcaptcha.com/overview\n"], "modules": [{"name": "indico_cloud_captchas", "documentation": ["This file is part of the Indico plugins.", "Copyright (C) 2002 - 2024 CERN", "The Indico plugins are free software; you can redistribute", "them and/or modify them under the terms of the MIT License;", "see the LICENSE file for more details."], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "indico_cloud_captchas._", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "indico_cloud_captchas.make_bound_gettext", "xref": {"fqname": "indico.util.i18n.make_bound_gettext", "project": "indico"}}]}, {"name